title: 2015.ISDE.International.Six.Day.Enduro.SPEEDHD.720p.H264.Englis
description: The Slovak Motorcycling Federation (SMF), under patronage of the International Motorcycle Federation (FIM), organised the 90th edition of the International Six Days of Enduro 2015 (ISDE). The Six Days of Enduro, even know as the "Moto Olympics", is a unique event hosted each year in a different Country, to assign the title of Enduro World Champion for National Teams. This was the fifth time in its history that the ISDE was held in Slovakia. From 7th to 12th September over five hundred and fifty riders from up to thirty-five countries gathered in the host city of Kosice in Eastern Slovakia
